1
00:00:00,320 --> 00:00:04,335
How to install MetaMask
on smartphone/tablet?

2
00:00:04,413 --> 00:00:09,132
Open "Play Store"
or "App Store" if you have an iPhone/iPad

3
00:00:09,499 --> 00:00:12,458
In the search bar look for
"MetaMask"

4
00:00:16,645 --> 00:00:20,650
Install it

5
00:00:20,675 --> 00:00:25,229
then open it

6
00:00:29,474 --> 00:00:33,216
Click on "Get started"

7
00:00:33,388 --> 00:00:38,723
In this guide we select "Import..."
because we want to have

8
00:00:38,748 --> 00:00:43,652
the same public address like
on computer, right? :)

9
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:47,849
Type in your secret phrase,
that you've received

10
00:00:47,874 --> 00:00:52,091
installing MetaMask on computer

11
00:00:52,404 --> 00:00:57,885
You can select "Enable..."

12
00:00:59,903 --> 00:01:03,668
No tour, thanks

13
00:01:04,169 --> 00:01:10,428
Now you can see tha same public key
like the one on your computer

14
00:01:12,154 --> 00:01:18,818
Click on "Browser"

15
00:01:19,834 --> 00:01:27,388
Then in the address field
type in our website's address:

16
00:01:27,413 --> 00:01:37,094
www.god-s-world.net

17
00:01:48,345 --> 00:01:56,024
Click on "Enter",
then "Sign up with MetaMask"

18
00:01:58,407 --> 00:02:02,689
"Connect"

19
00:02:04,707 --> 00:02:08,986
"Sign"

20
00:02:11,427 --> 00:02:15,587
Now, at the bottom of the page
you can see the first and the last chars

21
00:02:15,612 --> 00:02:18,669
of your public key

22
00:02:19,203 --> 00:02:23,875
The same you can see at the top
From now on your progress will be saved

23
00:02:24,219 --> 00:02:26,617
Congratulations!

24
00:02:26,859 --> 00:02:28,843
Have fun!

